---
import styles from '../../pages/projects/museum-label-generator.module.css';
const s = styles;
---

<div class={s['header-visual']}>
  <div class={s['artwork-display']}>
    <div class={s['artwork-frame-wrap']} id="artworkFrameWrap">
      <div class={s['artwork-stage']} id="artworkStage">
        <div class={s['artwork-loading']} id="artworkLoading">
          <svg class={s['artwork-loading-icon']} viewBox="0 0 48 48" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="10" y="8" width="28" height="32" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <path d="M15 31l7-8 5 5 4-4 4 7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            <circle cx="30" cy="17" r="3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/deqij2maw/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,w_1600/portfolio/frame" alt="" class={s['frame-img']} aria-hidden="true" />
      <span id="artworkPauseIndicator" style="position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;z-index:10;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.2s ease;pointer-events:none;font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:0.58rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(250,248,245,0.92);background:rgba(0,0,0,0.38);padding:3px 8px">Paused</span>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:0.4rem 0 0;text-align:center">Click to pause · Double-click to resume</p>
  </div>

  <div class={s['wall-label-card']}>
    <span class={s['wlc-eyebrow']}>Wall Label</span>
    <div class={s['wlc-title']} id="wlc-title">Untitled</div>
    <div class={s['wlc-meta']} id="wlc-meta">Artist unknown · Date unknown</div>
    <p class={s['wlc-body']} data-placeholder id="wlc-body">Famille noire porcelain exemplifying the Kangxi period's apotheosis of ferric oxide reduction firing, the pictorial program articulating a syncretic cosmological schema through the deployment of peony, prunus, and corvid iconography within a horror vacui compositional field. <b>Wait, what? Use the generator.</b></p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
import { init as initRotator } from './artworkRotator';
initRotator();
</script>
